javax.batch.runtime.context

Interface FlowResults


  • public interface FlowResults
    The FlowResults object identifies a flow and its batch and exit status. It is used by the SplitContext.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      JobOperator.BatchStatus getBatchStatus()
      The getBatchStatus method returns the batch status value of the flow.
      String getExitStatus()
      The getExitStatus method returns the exit status value of the flow.
      String getFlowId()
      The getFlowId method returns the value of the flow element's id attribute.
